<br>
But that's not how it works on my server.  You can post until you turn blue and your fingers fall off, but it's not how it is on my server.<br>
<br>
-Crowns from PoA cost 100k to 150k on my server<br>
-All mage spells always sell for huge pp when they first come out.<br>
-Many mages I know would let you die and finish off your mob if they thought it had something they wanted on it.<br>
<br>
Sounds ugly right?  Yeah it is.  I have been pissed about it for years.  But I can either deal with it, or I can just be angry at a game that I'm supposed to be enjoying.  So I choose to deal with it, and remain happy.<br>
